'''培根大爆炸'''（{{lang-en|Bacon Explosion}}）是一道[[美式足球|美式足球]]大小的特大號[[豬肉|豬肉]]料理，以厚切[[培根|培根]]片包裹辣味[[香腸|香腸]]和培根絞肉餡，以[[燻|煙燻]]或[[烘焙|烘烤]]而成。

它被張貼上燒烤迷網站「BBQ Addicts」後，在網路上引起轟動，不久便被主流媒體大幅報導，紅遍英美<ref name="NYTimes">{{cite news |first=Damon |last=Darlin |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |title=Take Bacon. Add Sausage. Blog. |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/28/dining/28bacon.html |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2009-01-28 |archive-date=2009-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130125138/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/28/dining/28bacon.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》稱它是「網路上最火紅的美食」，也是一道熱量高達5000[[卡路里|卡路里]]的創意燒烤料理<ref name="Telegraph" />。

== 起源 ==
2008年12月，傑森·戴（Jason Day）和艾倫·克洛尼斯特（Aaron Chronister）將培根大爆炸的食譜貼在燒烤迷網站「BBQ Addicts」上後，旋及造成一股「網路現象」<ref>{{cite web |first=Jason |last=Day |work=BBQ Addicts |title=Bacon Explosion: The BBQ Sausage Recipe of all Recipes |url=http://www.bbqaddicts.com/blog/recipes/bacon-explosion/ |date=2008-12-23 |accessdate=2009-01-28 |archive-date=2009-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201015007/http://www.bbqaddicts.com/blog/recipes/bacon-explosion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它在短時間內吸引了超過50萬次點閱和1萬6千條連結，甚至被轉載到政治網站上，因為「[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨人]]愛吃肉」<ref name="NYTimes" /><ref name="Telegraph">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/foodanddrinknews/4399224/Bacon-Explosion-recipe-is-most-popular-on-the-web.html |title=Bacon Explosion recipe is most popular on the web |first=Anita |last=Singh |date=2009-01-30 |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |accessdate=2009-01-31 |archive-date=2009-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090131160112/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/foodanddrinknews/4399224/Bacon-Explosion-recipe-is-most-popular-on-the-web.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{efn|1 = 參見[[專欄作家|專欄作家]][[約拿·戈登堡|約拿·戈登堡]]（Jonah Goldberg）在他的個人網站上的評論：[http://corner.nationalreview.com/post/?q=NDljMGRiOGVlZTY3OTJkMzVjNTA5YzNhNTQ0ZjI1ZTQ= 培根大爆炸]。}}。在[[網路爆紅|網路爆紅]]後，以培根大爆炸為名的粉絲俱樂部紛紛成立，視頻網站上也出現許多拍攝料理製作的錄影帶。

培根大爆炸的發明人是來自[[堪薩斯城_(密蘇里州)|堪薩斯城]]的燒烤高手，以「焦手指燒烤隊」為名，組隊參加燒烤競賽。他們在完成一道終極培根料理的挑戰下，終於想出這道佳餚，並取名為「培根大爆炸：燒烤香腸料理的極致」。<ref name="Telegraph" />

培根大爆炸和許多美國料理十分雷同，戴和克洛尼斯特也沒有宣稱他們是料理的發明人<ref name="NYTimes" />。在2008年12月以前，「無頭網站」張貼了一份稱為「終極肥胖」（Ultimate Fattie）的食譜，以[[香腸|香腸]]、[[辣椒|辣椒]]、[[莎樂美腸|莎樂美腸]]和[[芒斯特芝士|芒斯特芝士]]等食材做內餡，捲入格狀交錯而成的培根切片<ref name="Headless">{{cite web |title=The Ultimate Fattie |date=2008-12-14 |accessdate=2009-02-07 |work=Headless Blogger |url=http://headlessblogger.blogspot.com/2008/12/ultimate-fattie.html |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811102545/http://headlessblogger.blogspot.com/2008/12/ultimate-fattie.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這道混合料理的想法則是來自「美食捲網站」上的培根起司捲<ref name=Headless/><ref>{{cite web |title=Bacon and Cheese Roll |date=2008-11-28 |url=http://foodproof.com/photos/view/bacon-cheese-roll-1290 |work=FoodProof |accessdate=2009-02-07 |archive-date=2009-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205053611/http://foodproof.com/photos/view/bacon-cheese-roll-1290 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 流行與普及 ==
培根大爆炸的高人氣，除了發源地美國和英國外，也吸引德國和荷蘭媒體爭相報導<ref>{{cite web | title = 'Bacon Explosion': Dieses Grill-Monster erobert das Internet | work =  | publisher = Express | date = 2009-01-30 | url = http://www.express.de/ratgeber/living/dieses-grill-monster-erobert-das-internet/-/2484/788526/-/index.html | doi =  | accessdate = 2009-02-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110809233654/http://www.express.de/ratgeber/living/dieses-grill-monster-erobert-das-internet/-/2484/788526/-/index.html | archivedate = 2011-08-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last = Plas | first = Caroline van der | title = Bacon Explosion dé hit op internet | date = 2009-01-31 | publisher = Meat & Meal | url = http://www.bbqwijzer.nl/content/view/69/60/ | doi =  | accessdate = 2009-02-03 | archive-date = 2020-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201129132659/https://www.bbqwijzer.nl/content/view/69/60/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。其中，它的高卡路里和高脂肪飽受眾多評論批評。許多探討美國人健康或肥胖議題的主流刊物便抓緊機會，指出像培根大爆炸之類的菜色是「美國人肥胖的原因」，其他報章雜誌亦表示它絕對不是醫生會推薦食用的佳餚<ref>{{cite news |title=The 'Bacon Explosion': Why Americans are fat |first=Yael T. |last=Abouhalkah |date=2009-01-29 |accessdate=2009-01-31 |url=http://voices.kansascity.com/node/3497 |work=Kansas City Star |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090131161407/http://voices.kansascity.com/node/3497 |archivedate=2009-01-31 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Super Bowl Foods the Doc Won't Recommend |first=Monica |last=Nista |coauthors=Lauren Cox |date=2009-01-30 |url=http://www.abcnews.go.com/Health/Diet/story?id=6759625&page=1 |accessdate=2009-01-31 |work=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] |archive-date=2009-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202060640/http://abcnews.go.com/Health/Diet/story?id=6759625&page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，培根大爆炸也常被用於[[Web_2.0|Web 2.0]]技術的相關舉例（克洛尼斯特是一位網路行銷者）<ref>{{cite news |title=Bacon Explosion: An Artery-Clogging Example Of Web 2.0 Strategies |date=2009-01-29 |first=Matthew |last=Bandyk |url=http://www.usnews.com/blogs/risky-business/2009/1/29/bacon-explosion-an-artery-clogging-example-of-web-20-strategies.html |work=US News and World Report |accessdate=2009-02-03 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20090201035036/http://www.usnews.com/blogs/risky-business/2009/1/29/bacon-explosion-an-artery-clogging-example-of-web-20-strategies.html |archive-date=2009-02-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 製作 ==
根據培根大爆炸的介紹，它的製作過程「僅需要最低限度的烹飪才華」，而且備料十分簡單。食材包括：厚切培根910克、[[義大利香腸|義大利香腸]]910克、[[燒烤醬|燒烤醬]]一罐以及適量的調味料。<ref name=Telegraph/>

培根首先編織成格紋狀，準備進行調味。完成調味後，在培根上方鋪上一層香腸肉，再以培根絞肉點綴。接著，在肉餚表面塗上燒烤醬，並補足燒烤調味料，隨後捲起，塑形成巨大的捲狀。肉捲根據厚度而有不同的烹烤時間，每英吋約需一小時。在燒烤時，可適量補充燒烤醬。肉捲烤熟後，切片，即可享用。<ref name=Telegraph/>

完整一道培根大爆炸料理的熱量高達5000[[卡路里|卡路里]]（2.1萬[[焦耳|千焦耳]]），並含有至少500克的脂肪。即使僅取用一人份（約8盎司），也有878卡路里和60克的脂肪<ref>{{cite web|title=Bacon Explosion by Weight - Nutrition Facts - Heads Up Eating|url=http://www.headsupeating.com/nutrition-facts/+Bacon+Explosion/18385/|access-date=2011-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331073138/http://www.headsupeating.com/nutrition-facts/+Bacon+Explosion/18385/|archive-date=2012-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

