培根大爆炸在竄紅後，相繼出現許多改造料理。例如，「培根大爆炸重遊」便在原食材加入維菲塔乳酪（velveeta）和其他三種肉類<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tipsforbbq.com/Recipes/Pork/BaconExplosionRevisited |title=Bacon Explosion Revisited (aka Pork Pinwheels) |work=tipsforbbq.com |date=2011-04 |accessdate=2011-08-05 |archive-date=2012-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113032830/http://tipsforbbq.com/Recipes/Pork/BaconExplosionRevisited |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有的版本則選用墨西哥青辣椒和雞蛋<ref>{{cite web |author=George |url=http://www.gourmetfoodgarden.com/wordpress/how-to-build-a-better-bacon-explosion/ |title=How To Build A Better Bacon Explosion |work=Gourmet Food Garden Blog |date=2009-05-08 |accessdate=2011-08-05 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109092501/http://www.gourmetfoodgarden.com/wordpress/how-to-build-a-better-bacon-explosion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Robyn |url=http://grillgrrrl.com/2011/05/bacon-explosion-on-the-big-green-egg/ |title=Bacon Explosion on the Big Green Egg |work=Grill Grrrl Blog |date=2011-05-03 |accessdate=2011-08-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120714152238/http://grillgrrrl.com/2011/05/bacon-explosion-on-the-big-green-egg/ |archivedate=2012-07-14 }}</ref>，創造不同風味的培根大爆炸。

